message.body: If its too hard to make it here in the morning in the snow, I'm free the next two Saturday mornings! :)
I had such a rough night last night. And with a reason, its my moon time. So needless to say I'm feeling weakish..I do have rehearsal for The Vagina Mono
logues for the next couple of Sat. So i may have to cut out at 11:30a. But let's meet next week So sorry to disappoint us both
Hi Darlene, That's totally ok. See you next week! I understand moon time!!!
One thing I'm grateful for is that we both understand and accept each others needs and are flexible! That's really important for me at this point in my life!
